data.description: This 2017 custom built rare 4 Bdrm 3 full Bath home is a spacious and charming four-year-old property perfect for a growing family or hosting guests. As you approach the home within this quiet cul-de-sac you are greeted by a lovely front porch that provides a warm and welcoming entryway with stone and brick features. The front yard is beautifully landscaped creating a picture-perfect curb appeal. Inside the home, you will find a formal dining area perfect for hosting dinner parties or enjoying family meals, right next to that you find this tucked away office, great for privacy. The kitchen features plenty of counter space, a large island perfect for preparing meals or entertaining guests. The kitchen also boasts modern appliances and plenty of cabinet space for storage. The home has four bedrooms with the one on the main, providing ample space for a large family or for accommodating guests or friends. Each bedroom is well-appointed and offers comfortable accommodations with three full baths. The master bedroom features a spacious en-suite bathroom with a luxurious bathtub and a separate shower. The 3 bathrooms throughout the home ensures that everyone has their own space and privacy. Don’t let me forget one of the standout features of the home is the arches of the  main floor room entrances.  The lot is very deceiving offering a larger backyard space opening up possibilities for outdoor living space much beyond a single family backyard.
